CommentBody:
the customer is from APAC

customer is on unsupported SA and AIC 11.0 version and looks like they have issues with the SQL server connectivity

it shows in screenshot in Activity Monitor, but not AIC.
StealthAUDIT FSAC scan and import job should be checked as this is the component to make it available in the database for AIC to view.

TSMC has a custom job for Isilon, if this is Isilon it may require assistance after collecting job logs, as there is a pre scan process job to merge tsv files together prior to scan import.
A similar issue is reported on : https://nwxcorp.lightning.force.com/lightning/r/Case/5004u00002rlAHhAAM/view
